Requirement:
Simple Salestax calculation project.

Salextax will be calculated at a rate of 10% for all products except Books,Medicines and Food.
ImportTax will be calculated at a rate of 5% for all products without any exceptions.

The tax calculated will be rounded or to nearest 0.05 and added to the product price.

Solution:

Considerations : Every Order will have a list of products, for which the sales tax will be calculated.

